   Karron, Jeffrey D.; Flanagan, Rebecca J., Univ Wisconsin, Dept Biol Sci, Milwaukee, WI 53201 USA.
   Holmquist, Karsten G., Univ Wisconsin, Dept Hort, USDA ARS, Vegetable Crops Res Unit, Madison, WI 53706 USA.
